          h3 Sprig Optimization
          :marked
              ```
              $ sprig 'file_name' /folder/master.Jade
              ```

              * 1. creates file 'file_name.jade' next to master.
              * 2. Inside master create a list item ```li (file_name)[#file_name]
              * 3. Inject content block into master.Jade
              * 4. file_name.jade has content for to be a content block injected into master.jade
              * 5. file_name.jade has h3 title 'file_name'
              * 6. open in my editor master.jade & file_name.jade 
